snippet.title: Cancelled 16-bit Mickey "Doom" Game Uncovered - Why Disney
snippet.description:
I started coding this SEGA Genesis/MD game in 1994 - In this video I look at the coding tricks used and why Disney cancelled it

Link to Toy Story 3D explanation - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OL3cuHoquUk
